casebody.head_matter:
SOUTH CAROLINA, petitioner,
v.
Kamell D. EVANS.
No. 15-882.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 18, 2016.
Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Common Pleas of South Carolina, Greenville County denied.
